org.bonitasoft.engine.operation

Class LeftOperandBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bonitasoft.engine.operation.LeftOperandBuilder

  • public class LeftOperandBuilder
extends Object
    Builder for LeftOperand. LeftOperand is part of the Operation framework. A LeftOperand have a name, which is a reference to a data / variable, or a document. The value of the reference is evaluated at runtime, according to the Operation context.
    Author:
    Zhang Bole, Emmanuel Duchastenier, Baptiste Mesta
    See Also:
    Operation, OperationBuilder
